\end{enumerate}

\textbf{Common Bugs}
\begin{itemize}
    \item If your critic loss curves remain flat throughout training, make sure the critics are being updated.
    \item If your critic losses become very large, make sure the dimensions of your critic p redictions and targets are correct, and/or tensor broadcasting is done correctly.
    \item Make sure all critics are updated each iteration, not just those corresponding to the two target critics that are sampled for computing Bellman targets.
\end{itemize}
